'''Raed Chikhaoui''' ({{langx|ar|رائد الشيخاوي}}; born 9 June 2004) is a Tunisian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[center-back]] for [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1|Tunisian Ligue 1]] club [[US Monastir (football)|US Monastir]] and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].

==Club career==
Chikhaoui began his career with [[ES Hammam Sousse|Hammam Sousse]] in the [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1|Tunisian Ligue 1]]. In February 2024, he signed for [[US Monastir (football)|US Monastir]].<ref name="koora1">{{cite web|url=https://www.kooora.com/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D8%B6%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D9%8A%D8%AE%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%8A/1304048|title=أعلن الاتحاد المنستيري، اليوم الخميس، تعاقده مع المدافع رائد الشيخاوي|publisher=Koora|date=1 February 2024|language=ar}}</ref>

==International career==
In March 2026, Chikhaoui received his first call-up to the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://maghreb-foot.com/%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%A8-%D8%B9%D8%AF%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D9%86%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%A6%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84/|title=تراقب عدة أندية أوروبية اللاعب رائد الشيخاوي|publisher=Maghreb Foot|date=19 March 2026|language=ar}}</ref> Two months later, he was named in the team's final squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/cy42jjj4gg4o|title=Tunisia boss Sabri Lamouchi leaves Ferjani Sassi out of World Cup squad|date=15 May 2026|website=BBC Sport}}</ref>

==Playing style==
Chikhaoui was given the nickname "The Watchtower" due to his height and his versatility, being able to play in the defense, the midfield and the attack.<ref name="assarih1"/><ref name="koora1"/>

